      "parameters": {
        "width": 700,
        "height": 1020,
        "content": "üì± Veo3 Instagram Agent ‚Äì Create & Auto-Post Reels with AI\nDescription:\nThis no-code workflow automates the full pipeline of generating and publishing Instagram Reels using Veo3 (via Wavespeed API). From prompt to post, it handles content ideation, short-form video generation, caption writing, logging, and even automatic publishing to Instagram via Blotato.\n\nPerfect for creators, brands, and marketers who want to scale content creation without needing to shoot or edit videos manually.\n\nüîó  Watch the full step-by-step tutorial on how to build this workflow:\nhttps://www.youtube.com/@Automatewithmarc\n\nüöÄ What This Workflow Does:\nTrigger via Chat or Telegram\n‚ÄÉStart with a simple message like:\n‚ÄÉ\"Make a reel for a luxury minimalist candle brand using calm aesthetics.\"\n\nAI Video Prompt Generation\n‚ÄÉUses GPT-4 to craft a visually rich, platform-optimized video description prompt.\n\nüéûÔ∏è Video Creation with Veo3 API\n‚ÄÉSubmits your prompt to Veo3 to create a short video (9:16 ratio, 8 seconds) with motion, tone, and trend styles.\n\n‚úçÔ∏è Caption Writing\n‚ÄÉAn AI agent writes an engaging and playful caption based on the video content.\n\nüìÑ Google Sheets Logging\n‚ÄÉStores prompt, video URL, caption, and status in a GSheet to keep track of all generated assets.\n\nüì§ Auto-Publish to Instagram\n‚ÄÉPosts the video + caption directly to Instagram using Blotato‚Äôs social media publishing API.\n\nüîå Tools & Integrations Used:\nOpenAI GPT-4 / GPT-4o for prompt & caption generation\n\nWavespeed API (Veo3) for video generation\n\nGoogle Sheets for tracking\n\nBlotato for scheduling & publishing content\n\nn8n for orchestration and automation logic\n\nüí° Use Cases:\nContent calendar automation for small teams\n\nTrend-based ad creation and testing\n\nUGC-style reel generation for e-commerce\n\nRapid ideation & creative experimentation"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    }
